snippet.title: Galactic Getaway Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a cozy, uncharted planet and make it your own in this wholesome multiplayer life-sim! Befriend creatures to gather rare resources and build your dream home. Play fun minigames, farm crops, and craft decorations as you shape your perfect slice of galactic paradise!

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2012390/Galactic_Getaway/
Discord: https://discord.gg/kTy7jyKdqG
